The Civil Society Support Fund, is ex= cited to announce the launch of =E2=80=9CSOCIATHON=E2=80=9D which this year= will be a Visual Identity Design Competition under the patronage of the Mi= nistry of Social Solidarity, This initiative aims to raise awareness of the= Fund=E2=80=99s role and objectives in supporting civil society in Egypt. T= he competition offers a unique opportunity for creatives and designers to d= evelop a visual identity that embodies the Fund=E2=80=99s vision and goals,= which include providing financial, technical, and administrative support t= o civil society organizations.

= Win and Give Back: Your Chance to Shine and Make a Difference!

The winners' = prizes will be split equally between the winner and a charitable project of= their choice in Egypt. The charity work will be done in collaboration with= a civil society organization selected by the winner. The jury will choose = three designs to be showcased on social media for public voting to determin= e the best one.
